The floor of this boat is all aluminum so the floor will never get soft. The interior of this boat for it's age, is just fantastic and seats 14 people underway. The seats have been babied, being cleaned with murphys oil soap and a UV coating applied once per month during boating season. The carpet has no tears in it whatsoever and the sound system is new, along with the speakers. It comes with a 2007 Shorelander dual axle trailer  and the tires are like new condition. This boat is sitting in Port Clinton all bundled up for the winter and is waiting for you! Serious inquiries only.
